- buying service => SNS topic => Email notification, fraud service, shipping service v.v....
=> Pub/Sub pattern of Amazon SNS

- Up to 12,500,000 subscriptions per topic - not on exam
- 100,000 topics limit - not on exam

- two ways topic publish , direct publish

- SNS FIFO
	+ ordering
	+ de-duplication - id-based or content-based


- message filtering: JSON policy used to filter messages to SNS topic's subscriptions